    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You've seriously got to see this absolute beauty. It's been my pride and joy and honestly looks like it just rolled right off the showroom floor! Not a single scratch or smudge in sight\u2014it\u2019s been totally pampered since day one. If you\u2019re looking for that 'brand new' feeling without the dealership headache, this is definitely the one for you. Come take it for a spin, I promise you\u2019re going to fall in love!",
